Great!

8
00:02:13,710 --> 00:02:15,110
What's great about this?

9
00:02:16,470 --> 00:02:17,950
It looks prosperous,

10
00:02:18,380 --> 00:02:19,870
but it'll definitely

11
00:02:20,020 --> 00:02:20,990
cause chaos

12
00:02:21,270 --> 00:02:22,200
and more crimes.

13
00:02:30,310 --> 00:02:31,840
Lu Lingfeng, let me ask you.

14
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:34,480
Who should decide

15
00:02:34,500 --> 00:02:36,230
whether a policy is good or not?

16
00:02:38,070 --> 00:02:40,420
Policies should be in accordance with the law

17
00:02:40,420 --> 00:02:40,980
and

18
00:02:41,350 --> 00:02:42,810
be welcomed by the people.

19
00:02:43,750 --> 00:02:45,230
Who taught you

20
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:46,680
to be so smooth?

21
00:02:46,700 --> 00:02:48,230
You can't have it both ways.

22
00:02:48,420 --> 00:02:49,350
I think

23
00:02:49,590 --> 00:02:50,870
the public's opinion

24
00:02:50,980 --> 00:02:52,430
is the most important.

25
00:02:54,140 --> 00:02:55,829
Public opinion is important,

26
00:02:56,140 --> 00:02:58,560
but one cannot abuse power for personal gain.

27
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,960
The guy called Sima Liang

28
00:03:00,070 --> 00:03:00,890
is the sheriff

29
00:03:01,590 --> 00:03:03,590
and also the biggest wine merchant.

30
00:03:04,270 --> 00:03:05,580
An official is not supposed

31
00:03:05,580 --> 00:03:06,460
to do business.

32
00:03:07,110 --> 00:03:08,910
Who knows if he lifted the curfew

33
00:03:09,190 --> 00:03:10,190
for the people

34
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,470
or for his business?

35
00:03:12,350 --> 00:03:13,550
It's hard to say.

36
00:03:14,260 --> 00:03:15,070
Look at you.

37
00:03:15,230 --> 00:03:15,730
You…

38
00:03:15,790 --> 00:03:16,280
What?

39
00:03:16,829 --> 00:03:17,890
You have a problem?

40
00:03:18,829 --> 00:03:21,190
I'm just your personal secretary.

41
00:03:21,590 --> 00:03:22,590
I wouldn't dare.

42
00:03:24,510 --> 00:03:25,720
I'll denounce him

43
00:03:26,190 --> 00:03:27,790
to the magistrate tomorrow.

44
00:03:28,870 --> 00:03:29,710
Well,

45
00:03:30,550 --> 00:03:31,380
Sheriff Lu,

46
00:03:32,430 --> 00:03:35,329
as your personal secretary,

47
00:03:35,350 --> 00:03:37,030
may I give you

48
00:03:37,230 --> 00:03:38,630
a little piece of advice?

49
00:03:40,990 --> 00:03:42,120
Don't be sarcastic.

50
00:03:42,310 --> 00:03:42,840
Go ahead.

51
00:03:43,829 --> 00:03:46,350
The curfew has been lifted,

52
00:03:46,470 --> 00:03:48,600
and everyone's enjoying their night.

53
00:03:48,620 --> 00:03:49,560
Once you take office,

54
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,240
you try to bring the curfew back.

55
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,710
I'm afraid the people won't like it.

56
00:03:52,710 --> 00:03:53,970
As the old saying goes,

57
00:03:54,430 --> 00:03:55,890
don't retrace your steps.

58
00:03:57,230 --> 00:03:58,720
Keep this kind of nonsense

59
00:03:59,470 --> 00:04:00,930
to yourself in the future.

60
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,830
I'll go out for a walk

61
00:04:07,860 --> 00:04:08,990
with Yingtao later.

62
00:04:09,350 --> 00:04:11,520
We want to enjoy

63
00:04:11,550 --> 00:04:13,390
the hustle and bustle

64
00:04:13,710 --> 00:04:15,870
of Yunding's night market

65
00:04:16,350 --> 00:04:17,680
before you take office.

66
00:04:18,790 --> 00:04:19,390
You...

67
